Package aima.core.util.math.geom.shapes

Class Vector2D

  • java.lang.Object
    • aima.core.util.math.geom.shapes.Vector2D
  • public final class Vector2D
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a vector in a two-dimensional Cartesian plot.
    Simple arithmetic operations are supported.
    Author:
    Arno von Borries, Jan Phillip Kretzschmar, Andreas Walscheid
